              <p className="text-white/40 text-xs lg:text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
                Step 1: Configure settings and references.<br/>
                Step 2: Click "Generate Prompt" to review the AI strategy.<br/>
                Step 3: Confirm and render the final masterpiece.
